handist.mpijunit

Class ToFileRunNotifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.junit.runner.notification.RunNotifier
      • handist.mpijunit.ToFileRunNotifier

  • public class ToFileRunNotifier
extends org.junit.runner.notification.RunNotifier
    Custom implementation of the Junit RunNotifier. Instead of using the subscriber-based system of the standard Junit framework, this implementation writes the calls it receives received to a File specified as a parameter of its constructor.
    Author:
    Patrick Finnerty

      • close

        public void close()
           throws IOException
        Writes all the notifications received to the output stream objOut,flushes it, and closes it.

        This method should be called after all the tests have been run and the JVM running the tests for this particular place have terminated.

        Throws:
        IOException - if such an Exception is thrown when manipulating objOut
